"This gift card can not be redeemed since its code is not unique. Please "
"contact the organizer of this event."
msgstr ""
"Dette gavekort kan ikke indløses, da koden ikke er unik. Kontakt venligst "
"arrangøren."

#: pretix/base/payment.py
