"\n"
"with this email, we're sending you one or more vouchers for {event}:\n"
"\n"
"{voucher_list}\n"
"\n"
"You can redeem them here in our ticket shop:\n"
"\n"
"{url}\n"
"\n"
"Best regards,  \n"
